finnishquiz - small perl utility to practice finnish vocabulary (and other languages)

Usage:
    finnishquiz [options]

Options:
    -f --from=<lang>
    -t --to=<lang>
    -e --easy
    -g --groups=<number>

where <lang> is either finnish,spanish,swedish,english or catalan
and <number> is a natural number

This module needs Perl 5.10 or later.

Perl dependencies:
    Term::ReadLine
    Term::ANSIColor
    DBI
    DBD::SQLite
    Getopt::Long

